			<abstract>
				<p>Brief report by Erich Nasch, which became a part of the “documentation campaign” in Prague. Nasch describes the selection process
					in the Auschwitz concentration camp and the specific case of three Czech prisoners who managed to leave the camp in a transport
					which was sent to a labor camp.</p>
			</abstract>
		</profileDesc>
